Machine Learning và tạo model ML đơn giản¶

1. Machine learning là gì ?¶

Machine learning l lnh vc nh ca khoa hc my tnh, n c kh nng t hc hi da trn d liu a vo m khng cn phi lp trnh c th.

Thng thng, khi gii quyt mt bi ton theo cch truyn thng th cn phi xc nh c cc quy tc, cch gii quyt vn (la chn thut ton) v t vit code.

Nhng vi machine learning th khc, thay v phi xc nh cc quy tc, thut ton th chng ta cung cp cc cu tr li (labels) cho d liu u vo (data). Da vo , chng trnh s hc v a ra cch gii quyt cho bi ton.

Trong machine learning, th bn to ra t data v labels c gi l model. Tm li, chng ta c cc bc xy dng di y.

2. Xây dựng model cơ bản¶

By gi chng ta s tng bc xy dng mt model c bn.

Cng c: Python, Tensorflow, Numpy.

Tensorflow: l th vin m ngun m c pht trin bi Google, c s dng cho vic tnh ton s hc s dng th lung d liu.

Numpy: l th vin h tr cho vic tnh ton cc mng nhiu chiu. Numpy cc k hu ch khi thc hin cc hm lin quan n i s tuyn tnh.

Tuy nhin, i vi ngi mi tm hiu th vic ci t cc th vin kh l kh khn. C th thay th bng Google Colaboratory, mi th u c sn, rt thch hp cho ngi ang tm hiu v machine learning.

Cch s dng Google Colaboratory

Bc 1: ng nhp vo Google Drive.

Bc 2: Bm vo nt Mi.

Bc 3: Vi ngi mi s dng cha ti xung Google Colaboratory th lm nh hnh:

Bc 4: Lc ny mt ci bng hin ra, tm kim Colaboratory sau ti v

Prob: Cho bảng số liệu như sau¶

Quan st bng s liu, bn c th thy c mi quan h gia y v x l y = 2x. Cu hi t ra l c th d on c nhng gi tr tip theo khng ?

Nh gii thiu, vi machine learning, ch cn c d liu u vo (data) v cc gi tr u ra (labels) ca n th c th xy dng c cc quy tc, cc chun d on nhng gi tr tip theo.

Prac:¶

u tin chng ta cn import cc th vin cn thit vo.

Imports

Vic s dng Google colaboratory th c sn mi trng Python v Tensorflow s dng ri, chng ta khng cn phi ci t nhiu.

In [7]:
import tensorflow as tf
from tensorflow import keras
import numpy as np

Keras: Framework xc nh mng neural nh l mt chui cc layers.

Xác định và biên dịch mạng neural.¶

By gi chng ta s xy dng mt mng neural n gin nht. Mng neural ny c 1 layer v trong layer c 1 neuron.

In [8]:
model = tf.keras.Sequential([keras.layers.Dense(units=1, input_shape=[1])])

Tip theo chng ta s vit code bin dch mng neural. Chng ta cn 2 functions lm vic ny, l loss v optimizer.

loss: dng o chnh xc ca phng trnh d on (v d y = 4x + 1).

optimizer: a ra phng trnh d on, da trn gi tr m function loss a ra, function optimizer s a ra cu tr li sao cho gi tr ca function loss nh nht.

Vi Keras th 2 functions ny c sn, ch vic gi chng v s dng thi.

In [9]:
model.compile(optimizer='sgd', loss='mean_squared_error')

Nhập dữ liệu¶

Tip theo l nhim v ca th vin numpy.

In [10]:
xs = np.array([-3.0, -2.0, -1.0, 0.0, 1.0, 2.0, 3.0], dtype=float)
ys = np.array([-6.0, -4.0, -2.0, 0.0, 2.0, 4.0, 6.0], dtype=float)

Vic xc nh mng neural coi nh xong. Bc tip theo l train mng neural to ra model.

Training mạng neural¶

Qu trnh ny dng tm kim mi quan h gia x v y, a ra nhng d on (optimizer) v nh gi chnh xc (loss), lp i lp li vi s ln xc nh (epochs).

In [11]:
model.fit(xs, ys, epochs=500)

nhng ln lp u tin th gi tr loss cn kh cao, tc l phng trnh d on m function optimizer cha gn vi phng trnh chnh xc. Sau nhiu ln lp th gi tr loss gim dn, cng lc cng v 0. Tc l model ca chng ta d on ng mi quan h gia x v y.

Sau mt vi ln lp, gi tr loss gim dn cho n gn bng 0.

Vi bi ton ny th s epochs 500 l qu nhiu, khng cn thit. Khi m ch cn khong 70 epochs l model ca chng ta d on chnh xc ri.

Tóm tắt¶

C nhng khi nim c bn cn nm khi tm hiu v Machine learning.

Data: d liu u vo.

Label: u ra (hay cn gi l nhn).

Model: c to ra t data v label, s dng model d on nhng data khc.

Th vin numpy: mt th vin ton hc ph bin v mnh m ca Python.

Th vin tensorflow: th vin m ngun m h tr cho vic tnh ton s hc da trn biu m t s thay i ca d liu.

Loss: hm nh gi chnh xc ca gi tr d on.

Optimizer: hm a ra gi tr d on sao cho gi tr ca hm loss l nh nht.

Epochs: S ln lp khi train model.

Neural network: l mt h thng tnh ton ly cm hng t s hot ng ca cc neuron trong h thn kinh.
